<NEW>

RODIMUS straightened, and for a moment looked as if he were about to
walk right out that door, and then he took a step and kind of teetered
and had to catch the edge of his bed for balance.

"ACH!" He said as he put a hand to his head. "I feel fine, but my
internal gyro system as still a bit off." RODIMUS looked over at
WHEELIE as he carefully straighted again, this time a little steadier,
"What Maximal talks, what are you talking about, where are they?"

RODIMUS looked as if he would not like the answer. "The last thing I
remember was Tuscon trying to create a truce with the Predacons."

(TAG)
